n_2526228\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 13, 2022</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104bth1665702949940.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/bth1665702949940.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/bth1665702949940.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"bth1665702949940\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Environment Considerations for MySQL\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">\n</p>\n<section class=\"section\">\n<p class=\"p\"></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d545509e59\">\n                        \n Network Considerations\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bth1665702949940__p_d53414e1_d53415e1_d53416e1\">Both the Uniface Server and MySQL Server network capabilities can be used. The Uniface Server is used to connect Uniface to the connector, and the MySQL Server network capabilities are used to communicate between the connector and the MySQL Server database.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d545509e68\">\n                        \n Permissions\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bth1665702949940__p_d53420e1_d53421e1_d53422e1\">The MySQL Server installation program sets up permissions so that all users can read the necessary system tables by default. However, database owners can control the permissions on the system tables in their own databases. See your MySQL documentation for permissions on tables and databases.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d545509e77\">\n                        \n Unicode\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bth1665702949940__p_d53426e1_d53427e1_d53428e1\">The MySQL connector supports the use of Unicode in fields with a W packing code, table and columns names, user names and passwords, and in SQL. However, this functionality is disabled by default. To enable it, use the <code class=\"ph codeph\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"udi1665702731005.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/udi1665702731005.html\" title=\"Unicode is an industry standard designed to allow text and symbols from all languages to be consistently represented and manipulated by computers.\">Unicode</a>\n</code> connector option.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526228\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526228\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Environment Considerations for MySQL Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 13, 2022 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Environment Considerations for MySQL Network Considerations Both the Uniface Server and MySQL Server network capabilities can be used. The Uniface Server is used to connect Uniface to the connector, and the MySQL Server network capabilities are used to communicate between the connector and the MySQL Server database. Permissions The MySQL Server installation program sets up permissions so that all users can read the necessary system tables by default. However, database owners can control the permissions on the system tables in their own databases. See your MySQL documentation for permissions on tables and databases. Unicode The MySQL connector supports the use of Unicode in fields with a W packing code, table and columns names, user names and passwords, and in SQL. However, this functionality is disabled by default. To enable it, use the Unicode connector option. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}